      "html": "<p><span class=\"ann-font-serif\"><span class=\"ann-size-lg ann-font-mono\"><u><b>Note about Washroom Type II DI Water Systems:</b></u></span>&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><ul><li><span class=\"ann-font-mono\">NOT RODI. Should be considered non-sterile and may contain organic contaminates/microbes.&nbsp;</span></li><li><span class=\"ann-font-mono\">Do not use for incubators; instead use Type 1 Milli-Q or water produced for incubator use!</span></li></ul>",
      "when": "2026-04-10T13:53:00-04:00",
      "text": "Note about Washroom Type II DI Water Systems: NOT RODI. Should be considered non-sterile and may contain organic contaminates/microbes. Do not use for incubators; instead use Type 1 Milli-Q or water produced for incubator use!"
