    {
      "level": "info",
      "html": "<div><b><u><span class=\"ann-size-lg ann-font-mono\">High-speed centrifuge usage and care:</span></u></b></div><ul><span class=\"ann-font-mono\"><li>Pre-chill with the lid closed</li>\n  <li>After use, wipe out condensation and leave lid open to dry, remove rotor and lids and store properly on shelving, power down after use</li>\n  <li>Spills need to be cleaned up immediately - notify RF staff is there are any spills or consumable failures</li></span>\n</ul>",
      "when": "2026-04-10T13:56:00-04:00",
      "text": "High-speed centrifuge usage and care:Pre-chill with the lid closed\n  After use, wipe out condensation and leave lid open to dry, remove rotor and lids and store properly on shelving, power down after use\n  Spills need to be cleaned up immediately - notify RF staff is there are any spills or consumable failures"
    }
